    <p>Threat actors abuse supply chain and dev tooling. Oracle Cloud and GitHub Actions among recent cases. <a href="https://www.darkreading.com/threat-intelligence/dark-web-vendors-third-parties-supply-chains" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
    <p>Callback phishing scams using PDFs, QR codes, and fake support numbers impersonate Microsoft, PayPal, DocuSign. <a href="https://www.malwarebytes.com/blog/news/2025/07/microsoft-paypal-docusign-and-geek-squad-faked-in-callback-phishing-scams" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
